Package: CellWalkR
Type: Package
Date: 2023-12-1
Title: An R Package for Integrating and Visualizing Single-Cell and Bulk Data to Resolve Regulatory Elements 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given="Pawel F.", family="Przytycki", role=c("aut","cre"), email="pawel.przytycki@gladstone.ucsf.edu")
Description: CellWalkR is an R package that integrates single-cell open chromatin (scATAC-seq) data with cell type labels and bulk epigenetic data to identify cell type-specific regulatory regions. A GPU implementation and downsampling strategies enable thousands of cells to be processed in seconds. CellWalkRâ€™s user-friendly interface provides interactive analysis and visualization of cell labels and regulatory region mappings.
